SUBCONTRACTOR WILL PROVIDE SUPPORT IN DESIGN, DEVELOPMENT, TESTING, DOCUMENTING, HOSTING, SECURING, DEPLOYMENT AND OPERATIONAL MONITORING AND MAINTENANCE OF ALL SERVICES NECESSARY TO MEET THE USDA DAITSS EI-SUITE PROGRAM OBJECTIVES. SUBCONTRACTOR WILL SUPPORT APPLICATION DESIGN, DEVELOPMENT, SECURITY, MODERNIZATION, AND ENHANCEMENT, AS WELL AS APPLICATION OPERATIONS, MAINTENANCE, AND SUPPORT SERVICES.
